cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.CV

Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics): The paper presents a method for controlling a quadrupedal robot using imitation learning and model predictive control. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper uses a mixture-of-expert neural network architecture for policy learning. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper discusses the control of dynamical systems with a known model and the use of the Hamiltonian for optimization. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper presents an imitation learning approach for policy search. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition): Although not the main focus of the paper, computer vision may be used in the control of the quadrupedal robot.
